== 作曲 ==
歌曲由[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]、山姆·杜及[[杰克·安东诺夫|杰克·安东诺夫]]共同創作。歌曲的詞曲與電影主題相關，是一首電子R&B<ref name="ew">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/12/09/taylor-swift-zayn-i-dont-wanna-live-forever-ew-review|title=Zayn & Taylor Swift's 'I Don't Wanna Live Forever': EW Review|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly's EW.com|access-date=2016-12-10|archive-date=2016-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211142242/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/12/09/taylor-swift-zayn-i-dont-wanna-live-forever-ew-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>抒情歌曲。<ref name="rs">{{Cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/zayn-taylor-swift-team-for-sultry-fifty-shades-darker-song-w454824|title=Taylor Swift, Zayn Team Up for Sultry 'Fifty Shades Darker' Song|newspaper=Rolling Stone|access-date=2016-12-10|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142758/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/zayn-taylor-swift-team-for-sultry-fifty-shades-darker-song-w454824|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲中，贊恩使用假聲演唱，而泰勒絲演唱闡釋關係的部分。<ref name="rs"/>

== 樂評 ==
《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的诺兰·费尼指出：“一年以來的頭條並沒有給她（泰勒絲）的公眾形象造成打擊”“她正試著消除自己的爭議，而她也確實做到了這方面：『歡迎泰勒絲性感的一面』”<ref name="ew"/> [[Idolator|Idolator]]的四位編輯給予了歌曲3.5/10的評分。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.idolator.com/7653193/pop-perspective-zayn-taylor-swifts-i-dont-wanna-live-forever-review|title=Pop Perspective: Zayn & Taylor Swift’s “I Don't Wanna Live Forever” Rated & Reviewed  {{!}} Idolator|date=2016-12-09|newspaper=Music News, Reviews, and Gossip on Idolator.com|access-date=2016-12-10}}</ref>AXS的卢卡斯·维拉認為，這首歌不像[[埃利·古尔丁|埃利·古尔丁]]的{{单双书号转换|[[愛由你做主|愛由你做主]]}}或[[威肯|威肯]]的{{单双书号转换|[[你值得|你值得]]}}那樣性感，寫道：“儘管歌曲的歌词一般，但贊恩厚积薄发，设法向大众展示他最棒的表现。”<ref name=axs>{{cite web|last1=Villa|first1=Lucas|title=Review: Zayn saves tame Taylor Swift collaboration 'I Don't Wanna Live Forever'|url=http://www.axs.com/review-zayn-saves-tame-taylor-swift-collaboration-i-don-t-wanna-live-f-111439|website=AXS|date=2016-12-11|access-date=2017-02-10|archive-date=2016-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213015728/http://www.axs.com/review-zayn-saves-tame-taylor-swift-collaboration-i-don-t-wanna-live-f-111439|dead-url=no}}</ref>

